A light-weight RPC framework written by C. The name of this framework is rmi. It uses standard C header syntax for IDL. 

[rmiparse]
	This is the source code directory of the IDL compiler. It is written with flex and bison.
	
[librmi_src]
	This is the source code directory of rmi library.

[samples]
	This is the test directory.
	
[vsprojects]
	vs2008 projects for windows
	
linux平台编译过程：
1 执行make，生成librmi库和rmiparse编译器
2 进入samples各文件夹，详见里面的readme

windows平台编译过程：
1 用vs2008打开vsprojects下面的解决方案。
2 编译rmiparse工程生成rmiparse编译器
3 进入samples各文件夹，详见里面的readme
	
